Web Ecology Tool Kit - Twitter Collection Package

require 'pork'

Step 2: Establish db connection

WETK_Twitter::Planner.db_connect(db_config_yaml_file)

The db_config file should look like this:
adapter: your_db_adapter (ie. postgresql)
encoding: utf8
reconnect: false
database: your_db_name
username: your_username
password: your_password

Step 3: Authenticate for Twitter

WETK_Twitter::Planner.authenticate_twitter_user(username, password)

